metadata.name: Light vs Dark
metadata.description:
In "Light vs Dark" the eternal struggle between light and dark unfolds with intense emotional resonance. The canvas is alive with contrasting hues and textures, this two concepts, stand in stark opposition to each other. The light, elegantly clad in flowing white garments, radiates an ethereal luminosity that represents purity, hope, and enlightenment. It reflects serenity and determination, emanating an aura of goodness and virtue.

In striking contrast, the dark is cloaked in attire as dark as the depths of night. The blackness enveloping them symbolizes mystery, chaos, and the unknown. Their posture exudes an air of defiance, mirroring a complex mix of resentment, power, and hidden intentions. The dark coat, accentuate their enigmatic presence and intensifying the clash between light and darkness.

The confrontation between these two opposing forces is palpable, charging the atmosphere with tension and anticipation.
